1
00:00:03,720 --> 00:00:04,720
It's you.

2
00:00:04,760 --> 00:00:05,760
[Previously]
Too late.

3
00:00:06,040 --> 00:00:07,319
Your turn has come.

4
00:00:08,080 --> 00:00:09,399
Surround and kill this cur!

5
00:00:11,720 --> 00:00:13,119
I no longer need to disguise myself.

6
00:00:13,600 --> 00:00:15,039
You escorted the juniors here.

7
00:00:15,160 --> 00:00:16,160
You've truly worked hard.

8
00:00:16,560 --> 00:00:18,519
This is my "Certificate of Surrender."

9
00:00:19,200 --> 00:00:20,439
It is... Huang!

10
00:00:20,800 --> 00:00:22,759
What a magnificent gift.

11
00:00:50,080 --> 00:00:51,239
With this meager skill,

12
00:00:51,600 --> 00:00:52,639
you dare surround and kill?

13
00:01:16,320 --> 00:01:17,759
This little bull is forged from Immortal Gold.

14
00:01:17,960 --> 00:01:18,879
Capture it quickly!

15
00:01:18,960 --> 00:01:19,960
Present it to the Ancient Ancestor.

16
00:01:25,720 --> 00:01:27,479
Seems I was injured right down to my origin.

17
00:01:27,520 --> 00:01:29,359
There are many Dungyi Realm cultivators here.

18
00:01:29,400 --> 00:01:30,479
To escape and heal,

19
00:01:30,800 --> 00:01:32,119
I'll have to rely on wit, not force.

20
00:01:40,240 --> 00:01:42,199
"Raise the stone for a thousand days,
use it for one."

21
00:01:48,720 --> 00:01:50,399
It's your turn to take the stage.

22
00:01:53,560 --> 00:01:54,560
Hey!

23
00:01:54,760 --> 00:01:56,479
What's happening?

24
00:02:18,000 --> 00:02:19,359
The so-called "most dangerous place"

25
00:02:19,560 --> 00:02:20,919
is actually the safest place.

26
00:02:21,480 --> 00:02:23,039
I'll leave this little guy to deal with them.

27
00:02:23,520 --> 00:02:25,039
I'm going to borrow its cave to heal.

28
00:02:41,600 --> 00:02:43,119
This wound is strange.

29
00:02:43,920 --> 00:02:46,519
Could it be that the little bull's Immortal
Dao energy carried a complete Great Dao,

30
00:02:46,600 --> 00:02:48,039
injuring my origin so severely?

31
00:02:49,320 --> 00:02:51,039
Although I escaped just now,

32
00:02:51,280 --> 00:02:52,759
it's like adding frost to snow.

33
00:03:07,200 --> 00:03:08,719
That little fellow's cave...

34
00:03:09,440 --> 00:03:12,359
is actually formed entirely from
Yellow Dao Stones, which birth Yellow Dao Immortal Gold!

35
00:03:20,240 --> 00:03:21,839
This is still a primordial source land,

36
00:03:22,320 --> 00:03:23,479
brimming with infinite vitality.

37
00:03:24,040 --> 00:03:26,159
Could it be nurturing a new
Immortal Gold spirit?

38
00:03:26,880 --> 00:03:27,919
Gathering a whole nest, perhaps?

39
00:03:29,560 --> 00:03:30,560
Carvings, as I thought.

40
00:03:31,680 --> 00:03:33,159
This place wasn't naturally formed.

41
00:03:33,640 --> 00:03:34,919
It was artificially created with

42
00:03:34,920 --> 00:03:35,920
Immortal methods—a Life Pool.

43
00:03:36,480 --> 00:03:37,999
I wonder for whom it was prepared.

44
00:03:38,800 --> 00:03:39,999
Regardless, I've stumbled upon a bargain.

45
00:04:01,080 --> 00:04:03,279
This wound is actually generating deathly energy.

46
00:04:04,400 --> 00:04:06,359
If I don't absorb it using the
Secret Realm of the Wheel Sea,

47
00:04:06,560 --> 00:04:07,759
I fear it won't heal.

48
00:04:08,120 --> 00:04:09,759
The little bull gored me with a Dao wound,

49
00:04:10,040 --> 00:04:11,639
yet its cave brings vitality.

50
00:04:12,360 --> 00:04:14,079
Is this some kind of "Karma cycle"?

51
00:04:14,960 --> 00:04:16,239
Back in the Lower Realm,

52
00:04:16,400 --> 00:04:18,279
Little Tower often mentioned those two words.

53
00:04:18,720 --> 00:04:19,239
He even traded with me,

54
00:04:19,240 --> 00:04:20,599
risked everything because of it.

55
00:04:21,160 --> 00:04:22,559
Is it that the stronger one is,

56
00:04:22,880 --> 00:04:24,839
the more they are bound by
this invisible Karma?

57
00:04:25,200 --> 00:04:26,279
Little Tower was like this,

58
00:04:26,560 --> 00:04:27,719
and so was Willow Deity.

59
00:04:29,320 --> 00:04:30,320
You guys...

60
00:04:30,720 --> 00:04:32,039
where exactly did you go?

61
00:04:32,400 --> 00:04:33,959
Will there be a day we meet again?

62
00:04:35,960 --> 00:04:36,599
No.

63
00:04:36,960 --> 00:04:38,839
If there truly is an invisible force
blocking my path,

64
00:04:39,120 --> 00:04:40,239
I will simply sever it.

65
00:04:40,920 --> 00:04:42,119
The green rust from the Lower Realm's
Immortal Palace

66
00:04:42,160 --> 00:04:43,519
shattered my Great Dao origin once.

67
00:04:43,720 --> 00:04:45,319
I almost died and lost my Dao.

68
00:04:46,000 --> 00:04:46,639
This injury today

69
00:04:46,680 --> 00:04:47,759
means nothing in comparison.

70
00:04:48,160 --> 00:04:49,439
Though this injury is severe,

71
00:04:49,560 --> 00:04:50,639
hard to recover from,

72
00:04:50,840 --> 00:04:52,879
once I endure it, the rewards
will be immense.

73
00:04:53,200 --> 00:04:55,439
It might even trigger an all-around
transformation.

74
00:05:00,120 --> 00:05:01,919
My Immortal Qi is surfacing on its own...

75
00:05:02,120 --> 00:05:03,239
and it's so restless.

76
00:05:03,680 --> 00:05:04,680
Something's wrong.

77
00:05:13,080 --> 00:05:14,080
This is...

78
00:05:14,360 --> 00:05:16,199
The first wisp of energy that vanished
when I condensed Immortal Qi back then?

79
00:05:20,480 --> 00:05:22,559
When anyone condenses Immortal Qi
for the first time,

80
00:05:23,080 --> 00:05:25,559
they lose that first strand of Primordial Qi.

81
00:05:25,840 --> 00:05:27,919
But for you to actually glimpse its form...

82
00:05:28,640 --> 00:05:30,799
It's truly unheard of.

83
00:05:30,840 --> 00:05:32,639
The One begets the Two,

84
00:05:33,680 --> 00:05:34,759
the Two begets the Three,

85
00:05:35,000 --> 00:05:36,000
the Three begets all things.

86
00:05:36,240 --> 00:05:37,559
These three strands of Immortal Qi you have

87
00:05:38,120 --> 00:05:39,839
are all imprints transformed
from that first strand.

88
00:05:40,120 --> 00:05:43,039
If you forcibly keep the Primordial Qi,

89
00:05:43,440 --> 00:05:45,439
attempting to hoard everything,

90
00:05:45,560 --> 00:05:47,039
you will surely suffer backlash in the future.

91
00:05:47,720 --> 00:05:49,519
It will become a burden to you.

92
00:05:49,760 --> 00:05:51,119
This damn thing

93
00:05:52,080 --> 00:05:53,079
has been hiding inside me all along.

94
00:05:53,080 --> 00:05:54,599
Choosing this exact moment to emerge.

95
00:05:54,960 --> 00:05:56,479
Though it can mend my injuries,

96
00:05:57,720 --> 00:05:59,039
excess is just as bad as deficiency.

97
00:05:59,240 --> 00:06:00,240
It ends up harming my origin again.

98
00:06:00,360 --> 00:06:01,639
I wonder what the mystery of this pool is.

99
00:06:03,720 --> 00:06:08,759
It can actually nourish that strand of Primordial Maternal Qi.

100
00:06:09,400 --> 00:06:10,479
Since I can't avoid it,

101
00:06:11,160 --> 00:06:12,799
I'll figure it out and take it all.

102
00:06:12,823 --> 00:06:39,623
(Watch the Latest Donghua Episodes: www.h-donghua.xyz)

103
00:06:41,000 --> 00:06:42,319
Earlier, during the siege,

104
00:06:42,680 --> 00:06:44,359
I personally witnessed Huang suffer severe injuries.

105
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:45,600
His origin was damaged.

106
00:06:45,760 --> 00:06:47,199
This is a heaven-sent opportunity.

107
00:06:47,640 --> 00:06:49,079
We must take advantage of his wounded state

108
00:06:49,400 --> 00:06:50,439
to eliminate this future trouble forever.

109
00:06:57,680 --> 00:06:59,719
There must be a shocking secret at the bottom of this pool.

110
00:07:00,800 --> 00:07:01,800
I'm going all in.

111
00:07:02,200 --> 00:07:05,079
But what method can get me inside?

112
00:07:14,440 --> 00:07:15,719
It's that ball of flame.

113
00:07:42,080 --> 00:07:43,359
Immortal aura...

114
00:07:43,720 --> 00:07:45,119
What a terrifying restriction.

115
00:07:45,680 --> 00:07:47,079
It can even injure Divine Sense.

116
00:07:47,640 --> 00:07:48,919
In that case,

117
00:07:49,080 --> 00:07:50,479
I'll use the dragon scale as a shield.

118
00:08:13,800 --> 00:08:15,399
This entire war chariot

119
00:08:15,600 --> 00:08:17,359
is actually forged from Yellow Dao Immortal Gold.

120
00:08:17,960 --> 00:08:19,959
They're treating Immortal Gold like scrap metal.

121
00:08:24,120 --> 00:08:25,519
Golden horns,

122
00:08:25,840 --> 00:08:26,840
a bull's head...

123
00:08:27,120 --> 00:08:28,719
Why is there another Immortal Gold bull?

124
00:08:29,800 --> 00:08:31,839
These scars were all left by Immortal Dao energy.

125
00:08:32,480 --> 00:08:34,679
An Immortal bull is actually being used to pull a cart.

126
00:08:35,080 --> 00:08:36,119
They truly don't recognize quality.

127
00:08:36,440 --> 00:08:37,999
Could it be that the Immortal Gold bull outside

128
00:08:38,520 --> 00:08:40,559
used this place to resurrect via Nirvana?

129
00:08:41,640 --> 00:08:43,519
Perhaps I can make use of this as well.

130
00:09:32,040 --> 00:09:33,679
He is the master of the Immortal Bull.

131
00:09:34,560 --> 00:09:35,919
What an imposing aura.

132
00:09:38,160 --> 00:09:39,759
Why does this senior look so familiar?

133
00:09:57,360 --> 00:09:58,959
It's the Six Paths Reincarnation Immortal King!

134
00:09:59,560 --> 00:10:01,239
Is this the battlefield of the Immortal Ancient era?

135
00:10:17,440 --> 00:10:19,199
This is definitely not a power of the mortal realm.

136
00:10:19,880 --> 00:10:21,559
This man is an Immortal King.

137
00:10:23,000 --> 00:10:24,359
Yet such a powerful figure

138
00:10:24,800 --> 00:10:25,959
actually died here.

139
00:10:27,200 --> 00:10:28,599
I'm afraid we will never meet again.

140
00:10:43,320 --> 00:10:44,519
No Primordial Spirit...

141
00:10:44,640 --> 00:10:45,640
Could it be...

142
00:10:45,800 --> 00:10:47,399
that it was sucked away by this black hole?

143
00:10:49,440 --> 00:10:50,799
I should return to my main body first.

144
00:11:01,320 --> 00:11:03,199
Worthy of being the mother of the Three Dao Qi.

145
00:11:03,720 --> 00:11:05,319
What terrifying power.

146
00:11:06,080 --> 00:11:07,559
With the aid of this pool water,

147
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:09,000
using the body as the seed,

148
00:11:09,040 --> 00:11:10,079
and physique as the gate,

149
00:11:10,520 --> 00:11:11,919
the second Great Dao Fruit

150
00:11:12,240 --> 00:11:13,279
has finally condensed!

151
00:11:16,000 --> 00:11:17,319
This Dao Fruit governs slaughter.

152
00:11:17,640 --> 00:11:18,799
It is one with my very being.

153
00:11:19,360 --> 00:11:21,519
Once I wield it freely, my combat strength will surge violently.

154
00:11:24,200 --> 00:11:25,200
Oh no.

155
00:11:40,760 --> 00:11:42,559
The moment the second Dao Fruit was born,

156
00:11:42,920 --> 00:11:44,039
this calamity struck.

157
00:11:57,280 --> 00:11:58,280
Enough.

158
00:11:58,400 --> 00:11:59,559
I won't think about it too much.

159
00:12:00,040 --> 00:12:01,559
For now, focus on cultivation,

160
00:12:01,640 --> 00:12:02,640
and repairing my origin.

161
00:12:29,920 --> 00:12:31,719
What a terrifying marrow washing and bone replacement.

162
00:12:32,240 --> 00:12:34,039
They are actually using my body as a crucible.

163
00:12:34,200 --> 00:12:35,239
Immortal mist serves as the furnace fire,

164
00:12:35,240 --> 00:12:36,240
immortal mist serves as the furnace fire,

165
00:12:36,320 --> 00:12:37,759
and the bone marrow is the substance being refined.

166
00:12:38,200 --> 00:12:39,200
Such tempering—

167
00:12:39,880 --> 00:12:41,279
transforming the marrow into a great medicine for the human body,

168
00:12:41,360 --> 00:12:42,360
and then replenishing myself with it.

169
00:13:03,120 --> 00:13:04,120
Supreme Blood.

170
00:13:04,440 --> 00:13:06,119
Could it be growing another Supreme Bone?

171
00:13:11,800 --> 00:13:12,800
What a pity.

172
00:13:12,880 --> 00:13:13,880
It seems I thought too much.

173
00:13:15,120 --> 00:13:16,559
Rather than birthing a Supreme Bone,

174
00:13:16,960 --> 00:13:18,639
it's better for this blood to disperse throughout,

175
00:13:19,280 --> 00:13:20,280
nourishing my entire body.

176
00:13:21,360 --> 00:13:22,439
After consolidating it a bit more,

177
00:13:22,720 --> 00:13:24,239
I can charge into the Slay-Me Realm.

178
00:13:28,960 --> 00:13:30,679
The little fellow is back.

179
00:13:31,320 --> 00:13:32,719
It seems this place is unsafe to stay long.

180
00:13:35,120 --> 00:13:36,239
Huang is right here.

181
00:13:36,640 --> 00:13:38,439
Follow me to kill this little beast!

182
00:13:51,960 --> 00:13:53,119
You suffered a Great Dao wound,

183
00:13:53,680 --> 00:13:55,159
yet you can still block one of my palms?

184
00:13:56,120 --> 00:13:57,559
Fortunately, the Great Nirvana was perfect.

185
00:13:57,960 --> 00:13:59,559
To be fearless of a Dungyi Realm palm—

186
00:13:59,960 --> 00:14:00,919
with this physique,

187
00:14:00,960 --> 00:14:01,960
once I break through,

188
00:14:02,480 --> 00:14:04,319
I shall dominate those of the same rank,

189
00:14:04,520 --> 00:14:06,039
even those a realm higher!

190
00:14:08,600 --> 00:14:10,359
Merely a fluke, escaping once.

191
00:14:15,840 --> 00:14:16,999
Hand over your life!

192
00:15:23,320 --> 00:15:25,199
Now that the ultimate treasure is found,

193
00:15:25,720 --> 00:15:27,079
set out immediately.

194
00:15:35,520 --> 00:15:36,520
Great Elder,

195
00:15:36,960 --> 00:15:38,639
several batches of expedition teams have rotated out,

196
00:15:38,800 --> 00:15:39,999
but Huang still hasn't returned.

197
00:15:40,760 --> 00:15:42,519
With the异域 (Foreign Realm) stirring so fiercely,

198
00:15:42,840 --> 00:15:45,399
Huang's journey is far too dangerous.

199
00:15:45,920 --> 00:15:47,839
It is time to exit seclusion.

200
